# Root-level repo-meta Markdown — contributor/reference docs viewed on GitHub,
# not published Mintlify pages (none are in docs.json navigation). Excluded so
# the broken-links check doesn't flag their GitHub-relative links (e.g.
# STYLE_GUIDE.md -> ./CONTRIBUTING.md) or in-text link examples as page links.
# Docs pages are .mdx (including the index.mdx home page), so this only matches
# meta files: AGENTS/CLAUDE/GEMINI/CONTRIBUTING/STYLE_GUIDE/VERSIONING/README/…
/*.md
